## Limitations

The findings are based on a limited number of sources and may not capture the full spectrum of opinions on this topic. Additionally, the sources vary in their credibility and depth of analysis, ranging from academic papers to opinion pieces on social media platforms. Further research could include more empirical studies and data-driven analyses to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.